<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.4">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2024-11-01T12:46:47+03:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Jekyll-Theme-MDUI</title><subtitle>A Jekyll theme based on MDUI</subtitle><author><name>KeJun</name></author><entry><title type="html">Jekyll Theme MDUI Editor</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/living/2017/05/29/Jekyll-Theme-MDUI-Editor.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Jekyll Theme MDUI Editor" /><published>2017-05-29T19:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2017-05-29T19:00:00+03:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/living/2017/05/29/Jekyll-Theme-MDUI-Editor</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/living/2017/05/29/Jekyll-Theme-MDUI-Editor.html"><![CDATA[<p>静态博客在线攥写文章不是梦。</p>

<h2 id="功能">功能</h2>

<ol>
  <li>自动生成yml头</li>
  <li>markdown自动保存</li>
  <li>头图可直接预览</li>
  <li>随意添加或选择任意分类</li>
  <li>随意添加Tags</li>
  <li>更好的日期选择器</li>
  <li>随时编辑包括手机</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="使用">使用</h2>

<ol>
  <li>打开 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">https://yourblogurl/pages/editor.html</code>。</li>
  <li>按照提示填写对应信息。</li>
  <li>点击 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">CREATE FILE</code> 按钮。</li>
  <li>点击 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Download</code> 按钮。</li>
  <li>将下载的文件移动到 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_posts</code> 文件夹。</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">git push</code> 。</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="预览">预览</h2>

<p><a href="https://blog.kejun.space/pages/editor.html">demo</a></p>

<p><img src="https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2017/05/30/592d4280948fb.jpg" alt="" /></p>]]></content><author><name>KeJun</name></author><category term="Living" /><category term="mdui" /><category term="jekyll" /><category term="theme" /><category term="editor" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[静态博客在线攥写文章不是梦。]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Jekyll Theme MDUI</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/living/2017/05/29/jekyll-theme-mdui.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Jekyll Theme MDUI" /><published>2017-05-29T07:22:06+03:00</published><updated>2017-05-29T07:22:06+03:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/living/2017/05/29/jekyll-theme-mdui</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/living/2017/05/29/jekyll-theme-mdui.html"><![CDATA[<p>A Jekyll theme based on MDUI.</p>

<p>Material Design 设计，大部分配置使用 _data 文件，无需重启 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">jekyll</code> 即可完成配置。</p>

<h2 id="mdui">MDUI</h2>

<p>MDUI 是一套用于开发 Material Design 网页的前端框架。</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/zdhxiong/mdui">github</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://www.mdui.org/">MDUI</a></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h2 id="主题特性">主题特性</h2>

<ul>
  <li>响应式设计</li>
  <li>集成服务
    <ul>
      <li>Google 分析</li>
      <li>RSS</li>
      <li>本地搜索</li>
      <li>Disqus</li>
      <li>sitemap</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>多种独立页面
    <ul>
      <li>category</li>
      <li>friends</li>
      <li>search</li>
      <li>tags</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>纯 Liquid 压缩 html</li>
  <li>不依赖非安全插件（可直接部署到Github）</li>
  <li>PWA</li>
  <li>多样性 SNS</li>
  <li>在线编辑器<a href="https://blog.kejun.space/pages/editor.html">demo</a></li>
</ul>

